description: Returns all public keys whose private keys were used to sign the digest files within the specified time range. The public key is needed to validate digest files that were signed with its corresponding private key.

nested_items.name: PublicKeyList
nested_items.description: Contains an array of PublicKey objects.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The DER encoded public key value in PKCS#1 format.

nested_items.name: ValidityStartTime
nested_items.description: The starting time of validity of the public key.

nested_items.name: ValidityEndTime
nested_items.description: The ending time of validity of the public key.

nested_items.name: Fingerprint
nested_items.description: The fingerprint of the public key.
